channel.title: Old models
channel.description:
I made these a while ago, maybe a few years? and i was curious if i should get back into modeling purely based on these two models.
[IMG]http://i161.photobucket.com/albums/t205/Iammeyouarenot/fallensword.jpg[/img]
and
[IMG]http://i161.photobucket.com/albums/t205/Iammeyouarenot/newestsword.png[/img]
^^Part of the handle is missing cause i was lazy and figured the players hand would go there if i ever used it
I wouldnt mind getting better and if there is somebody who actually wants these im sorry but i do not hgave the model files anymore..
on a side note, Im new could somebody link me to metasque (cant remember spelling) or something that does the same thing?
